Deprecated API

Contents
  • Deprecated Methods
Deprecated Methods
com.swarmconnect.Swarm.addLoginListener(SwarmLoginListener)
          Please use SwarmUserManager.addLoginListener() Add a SwarmLoginListener. The SwarmLoginListener offers access to different stages of the user's login and logout process. 
com.swarmconnect.Swarm.isSwarmEnabled()
          please use Swarm.isEnabled() Checks if Swarm is enabled. Swarm is enabled if a user has logged in at least one time before (has accepted terms and conditions). 
com.swarmconnect.Swarm.removeLoginListener(SwarmLoginListener)
          Please use SwarmUserManager.removeLoginListener() Remove a SwarmLoginListener.
